import React from "react"
import { Form } from "react-bootstrap"

const FormColors = ({ name }) => {
  return (
    <>
      <Form.Label htmlFor="primary">Color picker</Form.Label>
      <Form.Control
        type="color"
        id="exampleColorInput"
        defaultValue="#563d7c"
        title="Choose your color"
      />
      <Form.Label htmlFor="secondary">Color picker</Form.Label>
      <Form.Control
        type="color"
        id="exampleColorInput"
        defaultValue="#563d7c"
        title="Choose your color"
      />
    </>
  )
}

export default FormColors
